<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0263a" xml:id="I01.0099.0263a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0263a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 99</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0263a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>建崇寺浮圖銘</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0263a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0263a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0263a0101">建崇寺</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0263b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0263b0101">亡祖秦州都酋長呂帛冰。女定羌女
<lb ed="I" n="0263b02" type="honorific"/><note n="0263001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩦾＝驃【史】</note><note n="0263001" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩦾【佛拓】，驃【史】</note><app n="0263001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩦾</rdg></app>騎大將軍南道大行臺秦州<note n="0263002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刾＝刺【史】</note><note n="0263002" resp="ihp" type="mod">刾【佛拓】，刺【史】</note><app n="0263002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刾</rdg></app>史
<lb ed="I" n="0263b03" type="honorific"/><note n="0263003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩕃＝顯【史】</note><note n="0263003" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩕃【佛拓】，顯【史】</note><app n="0263003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩕃</rdg></app>親縣開國伯亡伯興成。伯母帶神。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b04" type="honorific"/>龍驤將軍都督浙州<app type="star" corresp="#0263002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刾</rdg></app>史亡父興進。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b05" type="honorific"/>亡母元要。亡母男娥。亡母僧姿。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b06" type="honorific"/>亡叔法成。叔雙進。兄天猥。弟道伯。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b07" type="honorific"/>　　　亡<note n="0263004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">姉＝姊【史】</note><note n="0263004" resp="ihp" type="mod">姉【佛拓】，姊【史】</note><app n="0263004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">姉</rdg></app>李姿。<app type="star" corresp="#0263004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">姉</rdg></app>男姿。妹伯男。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b08" type="honorific"/>輔國將軍中散都督開國子宇文建。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b09" type="honorific"/>輔國將軍中散大都督宇文嵩。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b10" type="honorific"/>弟進周。　崇息雍周。法達。孫洪濟。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b11" type="honorific"/>崇<note n="0263005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31147"/>＝妻【史】</note><note n="0263005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31147"/>【佛拓】，妻【史】</note><app n="0263005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">妻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31147"/></rdg></app>王光容。息女舍徽。亥子明月
<lb ed="I" n="0263b12" type="honorific"/>息<app type="star" corresp="#0263005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">妻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31147"/></rdg></app>王花。　姪季和。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b13" type="honorific"/>姪子。孝子。順子恭保。和達。和善。和
<lb ed="I" n="0263b14" type="honorific"/>伯母王阿松。佐阿男。兄<note n="0263006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31146"/>＝妻【史】</note><note n="0263006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31146"/>【佛拓】，妻【史】</note><app n="0263006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">妻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31146"/></rdg></app>仵思妙。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b15" type="honorific"/>弟<app type="star" corresp="#0263005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">妻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31147"/></rdg></app>王遝輝。姪女仙輝。小輝。鏑女。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b16" type="honorific"/>弟婦權常妙。息<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">萬</unclear>女。　<app type="star" corresp="#0263004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">姉</rdg></app><note n="0263007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30404"/>＝赤【史】</note><note n="0263007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30404"/>【佛拓】，赤【史】</note><app n="0263007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">赤</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30404"/></rdg></app>女。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b17" type="honorific"/>佛弟子權法超。　妹皂花。妹明光。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b18" type="honorific"/>佛弟子王湛書。
<lb ed="I" n="0263b19" type="honorific"/>佛弟子權仕<note n="0263008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥧨＝賓【史】</note><note n="0263008" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥧨【佛拓】，賓【史】</note><app n="0263008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">賓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥧨</rdg></app>。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0263c00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0263c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0263c0101">惟建德三年歲次甲午二月
<lb ed="I" n="0263c02" type="honorific"/>壬辰<note n="0263009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㳉＝朔【史】</note><note n="0263009" resp="ihp" type="mod">㳉【佛拓】，朔【史】</note><app n="0263009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㳉</rdg></app>廿八日己未。佛弟子
<lb ed="I" n="0263c03" type="honorific"/>本姓呂。蒙大祖賜姓宇文建崇。
<lb ed="I" n="0263c04" type="honorific"/>夫靈象神容。遺形異品。毗倫
<lb ed="I" n="0263c05" type="honorific"/>讚道。<note n="0263010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05080"/>＝敷【史】</note><note n="0263010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB05080"/>【佛拓】，敷【史】</note><app n="0263010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">敷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB05080"/></rdg></app>五抽之<note n="0263011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31150"/>＝劫【史】</note><note n="0263011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31150"/>【佛拓】，劫【史】</note><app n="0263011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31150"/></rdg></app>化。<app type="star" corresp="#0263003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩕃</rdg></app>揚設
<lb ed="I" n="0263c06" type="honorific"/>教。斯疇百代。聚沙起塔。欲崇
<lb ed="I" n="0263c07" type="honorific"/>虛之妙旨。崇寔因業淺。又息
<lb ed="I" n="0263c08" type="honorific"/>別將法和。為國展效。募衝戎
<lb ed="I" n="0263c09" type="honorific"/>首。從柱國銚國公益州征討。
<lb ed="I" n="0263c10" type="honorific"/>因陣身故。是以削竭家珍。興
<lb ed="I" n="0263c11" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">越</unclear>福邦。造浮圖三級。石銘壹立。
<lb ed="I" n="0263c12" type="honorific"/>師子乙<note n="0263012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䨥＝雙【史】</note><note n="0263012" resp="ihp" type="mod">䨥【佛拓】，雙【史】</note><app n="0263012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䨥</rdg></app>。輙於冥積。採取將
<lb ed="I" n="0263c13" type="honorific"/>來之因。身骸分流。欲追之懷。
<lb ed="I" n="0263c14" type="honorific"/>竊<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">求</unclear>乙念之善。又願帝祚永
<lb ed="I" n="0263c15" type="honorific"/>隆。万國來助。普濟乙切。曠劫
<lb ed="I" n="0263c16" type="honorific"/>師宗。六道眾生。同登斯福。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
